Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter's diplomacy and White House security
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yljgc
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 23 Dec 1994
Jimmy Carter's diplomatic efforts, the security problems faced by the White House and the size of Lyndon Johnson's handkerchief are mused over by Alistaire Cooke.